post.description:
This endpoint allows the creation of multiple document types at once.
The request body must contain an array of document types to be added.
Requires API Key authorization.
            
### Request Example:
    POST /api/integrations/document-type
    {
        "tiposDocumento": [
            {
                "descricao": "NF-e"
            }
        ]
    }

Requires API Key authorization via the X-API-Key header.
Accepts a batch of up to 100 finance situation records in a single request.
            
**Request body example:**

    POST /api/integrations/finance-situation
    {
        "financeSituation": [
            {
                "code": 1,
                "description": "Active",
                "fix": false,
                "sell_operation": 0
            }
        ]
    }
